snippet.title: SRW X-Ω - Zombie Land Saga Debut PV (Saga The Great 7) l スパロボxω「ゾンビランドサガ」期間限定参戦記念PV (サガ・ザ・グレート７)
snippet.description:
Masami Obari designed the mech as a promotional image for the Zombie Land Saga OP & ED singles back in 2018. The mech did not even show up in the anime but God Obari managed to make this debut happen with just a simple promo image.
